# Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-
# ons manager
#: buildVars.py:17
msgid ""
"Provides enhanced terminal accessibility for Windows Terminal and "
"PowerShell, enabling screen reader users to efficiently navigate and "
"interact with command-line interfaces. Inspired by TDSR (Terminal Data "
"Structure Reader) and incorporates functionality from both TDSR and Speakup."
" Advanced features inspired by community suggestions and discussions."
msgstr ""
"Biedt verbeterde terminaltoegankelijkheid voor Windows Terminal en "
"PowerShell, waardoor gebruikers van schermlezers efficiënt kunnen navigeren "
"en communiceren met opdrachtregelinterfaces. Geïnspireerd door TDSR "
"(Terminal Data Structure Reader) en bevat functionaliteit van zowel TDSR als"
" Speakup. Geavanceerde functies geïnspireerd door suggesties en discussies "
"uit de gemeenschap."

#: buildVars.py:14
msgid "Terminal Access for NVDA"
msgstr "Terminaltoegang voor NVDA"
